---
title: Honey Haloumi & Roasted Cauliflower Bowl with Pearl Couscous
description: There was complete mayhem when this dish hit our tasting table. With sweet honey on warm, salty haloumi, plus chermoula veggies and toasty pearl couscous, it disappeared from the bowl in record time.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5ebcb950fb20c466cd267b31-37a5d0cc.jpg
